      <hedline>
        <hl1>Back of the Envelope</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Back of the Envelope column lists biggest hostile and unsolicited takeover offers involving law firm of Wachtell Lipton Rosen &amp; Katz (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The law firm of Wachtell, Lipton, Rosen &amp; Katz is a seasoned warrior in takeover battles. It invented the poison-pill defense. Now it has been hired by Caremark Rx, which is trying to fight off a $26 billion bid from Express Scripts in favor of a merger with the drugstore chain CVS.</p>
      </block>
